{"id":644422,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/【图说天朝】禁止明白让人明白/","date":"2020-05-15T11:25:58Z","modified":"2020-05-15T11:25:58Z","title":"【图说天朝】禁止&#8221;明白&#8221;让人明白","content":"<p>5月14日，南京象甲图书有限公司 @象甲书店 新浪微博发出“致歉信”，信中称该店的文创产品“明白”T恤被禁止销售，预售部分已全数退款。该书店并未写明T恤被禁售的具体原因，以及要求执行此操作的具体部门，此微博目前已被删除。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-644424\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EYDXK-0U0AE4G3--e1589539878482.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"911\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EYDXK-0U0AE4G3--e1589539878482.jpeg 992w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EYDXK-0U0AE4G3--e1589539878482-148x300.jpeg 148w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EYDXK-0U0AE4G3--e1589539878482-506x1024.jpeg 506w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EYDXK-0U0AE4G3--e1589539878482-768x1555.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EYDXK-0U0AE4G3--e1589539878482-758x1536.jpeg 758w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-644423\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/明白.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"644\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/明白.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/明白-233x300.jpg 233w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/明白-794x1024.jpg 794w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/明白-768x990.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/明白-400x516.jpg 400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>“明白”T恤被禁售的原因或来自李文亮的“训诫书”，对于警方“我们希望你冷静下来好好反思，并郑重告诫你：如果你固执己见，不思悔改，继续进行违法活动，你将会受到法律的制裁！你听明白了吗？”的提问，李文亮以“明白”作答。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-644425\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/明白.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"169\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/明白.png 1086w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/明白-300x101.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/明白-1024x345.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/明白-768x259.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/明白-1080x364.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>在李文亮去世后，有网民将李文亮训诫书上警方问询他的话语“你能做到吗？”、“你听明白了吗？”创建了话题#你能做到吗？你听明白了吗？#，表达对李医生的哀思和对当局的愤怒。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"3RgIqbmAEv\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e4%bd%a0%e8%83%bd%e5%81%9a%e5%88%b0%e5%90%97%ef%bc%9f-%e4%bd%a0%e5%90%ac%e6%98%8e%e7%99%bd%e4%ba%86%e5%90%97%ef%bc%9f/\">【网络民议】“你能做到吗？” “你听明白了吗？”</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【网络民议】“你能做到吗？” “你听明白了吗？”》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e4%bd%a0%e8%83%bd%e5%81%9a%e5%88%b0%e5%90%97%ef%bc%9f-%e4%bd%a0%e5%90%ac%e6%98%8e%e7%99%bd%e4%ba%86%e5%90%97%ef%bc%9f/embed/#?secret=3RgIqbmAEv\" data-secret=\"3RgIqbmAEv\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“你听明白了吗？”也一度成为新浪微博禁发词：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"kzd4tUYBq2\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e7%93%b7%e3%80%91%e4%bd%a0%e5%90%ac%e6%98%8e%e7%99%bd%e4%ba%86%e5%90%97%ef%bc%9f/\">【敏感瓷】“你听明白了吗？”</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【敏感瓷】“你听明白了吗？”》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e7%93%b7%e3%80%91%e4%bd%a0%e5%90%ac%e6%98%8e%e7%99%bd%e4%ba%86%e5%90%97%ef%bc%9f/embed/#?secret=kzd4tUYBq2\" data-secret=\"kzd4tUYBq2\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>而后，“不明白”作为关键词被纳入缅怀李文亮的画作。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/images/thumb/e/e1/Liwenliang3.jpg/800px-Liwenliang3.jpg\" alt=\"File:Liwenliang3.jpg\" width=\"556\" height=\"371\" /></p>\n<p>有网友讽刺称，当专制政权让你服从时，“明白”是正确的答案；但当专制政权让你遗忘时，“禁止明白”则是正确的答案。</p>\n","author":1001,"categories":[18271,38912,39486,39707],"tags":[40558,40560,39753,40561,40559,40026,40557]}